Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:24.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm happy as long as I can record your cute side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:27.20,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Airi was really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:31.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But what was she saying at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:34.74,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She even called Kozou-san by his first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:39.78,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's going on! No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:45.62,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This one's fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.02,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.49,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Both of them are cute anyway.\NShe'll be perfect. We'll have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:54.53,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah! We re going to have a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.29,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If we use this chick to call Airi, she'll come running.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:07.54,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,From here on out, let's go back to normal.\NLet's stop doing these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.81,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Okay, dad?
